<div class="wrapper wrapper_padding clearfix">
  <div class="col-1 about homepage_content">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <hr>
    <p>陳威齊 I'm a designer &amp; developer living in Colorado Springs,
    Colorado.</p>
    <p>By day I work as a front-end dev / designer at Precision
    Nutrition, by night I teach how to design &amp; code reails
    applications at <a href="http://www.el.cycu.edu.tw/wSite/ct?xItem=59028&ctNode=20241&mp=46002">繆紹綱</a>.</p>
    <p>You can find me speaking in 140 characters on Twitter,
    swooshing some pixels on Dribbble, and sharing some code on
    GitHub.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-2 homepage_content">
    <h2>Resources</h2>
    <hr>
    <% @notes.each do |note| %>
      <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to note.title, note %></a></h3>
      <p class="date"><%= note.created_at.strftime("%b %d, %Y") %></p>
    <% end %>
    <%= link_to "View More", notes_path, class: "view_more" %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-3  homepage_content ">
    <h2>Honor Roll</h2>
    <hr>
    <% @posts.each do |post| %>
      <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to post.title, post %></a></h3>
      <p class="date"><%= post.created_at.strftime("%b %d, %Y") %></p>
    <% end %>
    <%= link_to "View More", posts_path, class: "view_more" %>
  </div>
</div>
